Package com.purbon.pdfwriter

Basic PDF creation capabilities.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PDFWriter  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultPDFWriter
    Abstract PDF Writer, whenever you want to create a PDF this class is one of the main points of entrance to that library.
    PageHeader
    A Header for a PDF page.
    PDFContentPage
    A PDFPage that acts as a content/index page for a report.
    PDFDocument
    PDDocument extension including some new necessary functions that make PDFWriter more easy.
    PDFPage
    A PDPage extension with some useful addons that makes our work easy.
    PDFTitlePage
    A PDFPage that acts as a title page for our reports.
